How to play.....

Once you have started the game you see two dots or circles the green dot is snake
and the blue one is food. Whenever you eate the food you get 50 points.

To eat the food you have to navigate the head of snack to food. to move your
snake up press 'W', to go down press 'S' and press 'A' for left and 'D' for 
right.

Press 'P' to pause.

You may lose the game if you either hit the red baundary wall or the yourself(snake).

Press any key to continue.... 